{
  "stem": "14060.9",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Bricha or [INAUDIBLE]-- you know, the Israeli connection-- organized a mass emigration through various sources.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some through Kashau, Slovakia; and through Bratislava into Austria; and some through Hungary, through Szombathely.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Sopron, as well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I lived in Szombathely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my uncle, [INAUDIBLE] Arya Yahuda was his name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He died five years ago.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was born in 1906, and he went through Auschwitz, Buchenwald-- Auschwitz, Birkenau, ending up in Minsk, in Russia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because when Russians liberated, they took them the wrong way, back to Minsk, in January, '45.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he was the president.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My-- his father, my grandfather, was president for many, many years before the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he was in charge of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We had tremendous properties.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And one of the properties had two-- from the main square and the main street entrance.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So you could literally back in huge trucks and disappear, because there was high walls and high gates.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Nobody would know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I remember, day after day, only about 10 doors away was the-- this organization's office, local office, who looked after the immigrants or these refugees coming-- Romanians.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And constantly, every night, they just came quietly in in pairs, in twos and threes, into our property on one end, and they waited there till it became dark.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we had it organized with Russian military-- Jewish Russian military-- who were paid or not paid or whatever-- that night after night they were taking them out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So literally thousands, if not tens of thousands, of people went through that route.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I personally used to-- as a 17-, 18-year-old, it was after business hours, no problem.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was always at night, in the darkness-- I helped the people with their belongings, with their luggage.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometime, older people, to help them up on the trucks.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
